Configuration for [bspwm](https://github.com/baskerville/bspwm)
with [sxhkd](https://github.com/baskerville/sxhkd).

Also featuring [zsh](https://www.zsh.org/),
[qutebrowser](https://qutebrowser.org/),
[rofi](https://github.com/davatorium/rofi),
[polybar](https://github.com/polybar/polybar),
[dunst](https://github.com/dunst-project/dunst)
and [vim](https://www.vim.org/).

Rice based on the [base16-default](https://github.com/chriskempson/base16) colorscheme.
